{"id":"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations","title":"provideNoopAnimations","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser/animations\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser/animations\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\", \"name\": \"provideNoopAnimations\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations\">@angular/platform-browser/animations</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L124-L154\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts#L124-L154\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providenoopanimations\">provideNoopAnimations<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#providenoopanimations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">返回一組<a href=\"guide/glossary#provider\">依賴注入提供程式</a>以禁用應用程式中的動畫。請參閱<a href=\"guide/animations\">動畫指南</a>以瞭解有關 Angular 中動畫的更多資訊。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Returns the set of <a href=\"guide/glossary#provider\">dependency-injection providers</a>\nto disable animations in an application. See <a href=\"guide/animations\">animations guide</a>\nto learn more about animations in Angular.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideNoopAnimations</a></span>(): <a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[]</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <p>沒有引數。</p>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[]</code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">當你想使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 函式引導應用程式時，該函式很有用，但你需要禁用動畫（例如，在執行測試時）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The function is useful when you want to bootstrap an application using\nthe <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> function, but you need to disable animations\n(for example, when running tests).</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideNoopAnimations</a>()\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser/animations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Provider\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/animations\n - api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#providenoopanimations\n - api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - guide/animations\n - guide/glossary#provider\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L124-L154\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts#L124-L154\n-->"}